		  	<h1>The Best-In-Class Entertainment Experience Awaits You at Cine Cafes </h1>
		  	<p>Imagine enjoying delectable range of drinks & food of your choice while enjoying a movie or OTT show being screened exclusively for you and your loved ones in a plush interior with a luxurious seating arrangement! Isn’t something surreal and worth cherishing? </p>
		  	<p>At Cine Cafes, we made it easier for our guests to indulge themselves in a special screening of the latest movie or TV show in a private auditorium, meticulously designed employing state-of-art décor, furnishing, interiors and the best-in-class technology.</p>
		  <p>Our private screening facility is exclusively designed for group meetings (corporate or family), conferences, birthday parties, family or friends get together, which can be booked in advance through our app, website or over the phone. </p>
		  
		  <h2>Creating a Difference: The Cine Cafes Way  </h2>
		  <p>In order to ensure the safety of you and your family, we follow strict safety protocols, including thermal checks and social distancing enforced as per government norms. </p>
		  <p>At Cine Cafes, we are doing our part to help keep our guests safe by following extensive cleaning and sanitization protocols. </p>
		  <p>That means you are as safe as in your own drawing rooms with your close ones with the added magnificence of the big-screen cinema experience, high quality sound & an exemplary service. </p>
		  <p>There is not just a private screening space that we offer you but also an array of culinary treats & drinks for guests of all ages. Even in the pandemic era, we have seen a rise in the number of individuals, families and even couples visiting our place, and so, spending some quality time while watching a movie together with your family or friends is one of the rare experiences that we are proud to offer.</p>
		  <p>So why not book your own private screening space by downloading our app now? Please connect with us you have further queries. </p>
		 
